<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 21:12:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>派拉蒙斥资 84 亿美元收购 Skydance 面临美国权利中心 FCC 质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/paramounts-84-bln-skydance-merger-faces-fcc-challenge-by-center-american-rights-2024-12-17/</link><description>周二提交的一份文件显示，非营利性公共利益律师事务所美国权利中心已向联邦通信委员会 (FCC) 请求对派拉蒙全球公司和 Skydance Media 之间计划价值 84 亿美元的合并提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 18:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/paramounts-84-bln-skydance-merger-faces-fcc-challenge-by-center-american-rights-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国共和党委员会主席预计司法部将重启反华计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-republican-committee-chair-expects-revival-doj-counter-china-program-2024-12-17/</link><description>美国众议院国土安全委员会共和党主席周二表示，他预计司法部将重启一项重点打击中国间谍活动和知识产权盗窃的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 17:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-republican-committee-chair-expects-revival-doj-counter-china-program-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>据日经新闻报道，日本本田和日产将开始合并谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/japans-honda-nissan-talks-merger-amid-ev-competition-nikkei-reports-2024-12-17/</link><description>据《日经新闻》周二报道，日本汽车巨头本田汽车和日产汽车将开始合并谈判，因为它们面临着来自全球大型电动汽车制造商日益激烈的竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 17:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/japans-honda-nissan-talks-merger-amid-ev-competition-nikkei-reports-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>挪威向电池初创企业 Morrow 提供 1.34 亿美元贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/norway-grants-battery-start-up-morrow-134-million-loan-facility-2024-12-17/</link><description>政府机构创新挪威周二表示，挪威已向初创公司 Morrow Batteries 提供 15 亿克朗（1.34 亿美元）的贷款。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 16:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/norway-grants-battery-start-up-morrow-134-million-loan-facility-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大新年将对中国进口产品征收更多关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-impose-more-tariffs-chinese-imports-new-year-2024-12-17/</link><description>政府最新财政报告显示，加拿大计划最早从明年起对大量中国产品征收关税，作为对中国进口产品进行更广泛调查的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 14:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-impose-more-tariffs-chinese-imports-new-year-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>印度计划征收高达25%的临时税以遏制中国廉价钢铁进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-plans-up-25-temporary-tax-curb-cheap-chinese-steel-imports-2024-12-17/</link><description>行业和政府消息人士称，印度可能对钢铁进口征收最高25%的“保障税”或临时税，以帮助遏制来自最大生产国中国的廉价进口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 13:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-plans-up-25-temporary-tax-curb-cheap-chinese-steel-imports-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储会议、七国集团政治动荡，债券动荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 11:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾向南海军事人员发送物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-provisions-military-personnel-south-china-sea-2024-12-17/</link><description>菲律宾表示，本月早些时候已向驻扎在马尼拉占领但北京声称拥有主权的南海岛礁上的军事人员提供了物资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 11:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-provisions-military-personnel-south-china-sea-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>被英国称为中国特工的女子在针对军情五处的诉讼中败诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-loses-case-against-uks-mi5-over-spy-alert-2024-12-17/</link><description>伦敦一家法庭周二裁定，一名被英国军情五处认定为中国间谍的女子因向政界人士发出警告称她是为北京工作的特工而起诉该国内间谍机构，但败诉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 10:28:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-loses-case-against-uks-mi5-over-spy-alert-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>美银美林表示，投资者对美国股市的配置创历史新高，现金配置创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/investor-allocations-us-equities-record-high-cash-record-low-bofa-says-2024-12-17/</link><description>美国银行全球研究部 12 月的一项调查显示，本月投资者对美国股票的配置创下历史新高，欧洲股票、大宗商品和现金的配置有所下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 10:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/investor-allocations-us-equities-record-high-cash-record-low-bofa-says-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>外交部表示中方愿与印方通过边界谈判增进互信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-ready-enhance-mutual-trust-with-india-border-talks-foreign-ministry-says-2024-12-17/</link><description>外交部周二表示，中方愿同印方一道，通过对话沟通增进互信，真诚管控分歧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 08:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-ready-enhance-mutual-trust-with-india-border-talks-foreign-ministry-says-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>随着新排放规则的临近，欧洲汽车制造商对电动汽车打折，提高汽油车价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-carmakers-discount-evs-hike-petrol-car-prices-new-emissions-rules-loom-2024-12-17/</link><description>欧洲汽车制造商正在提高汽油车的价格，并准备对电动汽车进行折扣，以迎接另一个挑战——更严格的排放规定，这可能会进一步缩减整个陷入困境的行业的利润。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 06:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-carmakers-discount-evs-hike-petrol-car-prices-new-emissions-rules-loom-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国与特朗普畅谈美中合作前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-trump-talk-up-prospects-us-china-collaboration-2024-12-17/</link><description>在特朗普重返白宫之前，两个超级大国已经阐明了各自的立场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 05:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-trump-talk-up-prospects-us-china-collaboration-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国计划到 2025 年将预算赤字占 GDP 的 4% 创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-plans-record-budget-deficit-4-gdp-2025-say-sources-2024-12-17/</link><description>消息人士称，中国领导人上周同意将预算赤字提高至历史最高水平，同时维持 5% 左右的经济增长目标。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 04:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-plans-record-budget-deficit-4-gdp-2025-say-sources-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴将亏损 13 亿美元出售中国百货连锁店银泰百货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/alibaba-sell-mall-chain-1-bln-part-latest-overhaul-2024-12-17/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周二表示，将出售其中国百货商店子公司银泰百货，并因该交易损失 13 亿美元，因为这家零售巨头正在重组其业务组合，以专注于其核心电子商务业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 04:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/alibaba-sell-mall-chain-1-bln-part-latest-overhaul-2024-12-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>